---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { DefaultImage } from '../config'
---

<div class='relative overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-gray-900'>
  <div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl'>
    <div
      class='relative z-10 bg-white pb-8 lg:max-w-2xl lg:w-full dark:bg-gray-900 lg:pb-28 md:pb-20 sm:pb-16 xl:pb-32'
    >
      <svg
        class='absolute inset-y-0 right-0 hidden h-full w-48 translate-x-1/2 transform text-white lg:block dark:text-gray-900'
        fill='currentColor'
        viewBox='0 0 100 100'
        preserveAspectRatio='none'
        aria-hidden='true'
      >
        <polygon points='50,0 100,0 50,100 0,100'></polygon>
      </svg>
      <main
        class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pt-10 lg:px-8 sm:px-6 lg:pt-20 md:pt-16 sm:pt-12 xl:pt-28'
      >
        <div class='text-center sm:text-left'>
          <h1
            class='text-left text-4xl text-gray-900 font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-6xl sm:text-5xl dark:text-gray-100'
          >
            <span class='block text-purple-700 xl:inline dark:text-purple-300'>Astro Blog</span>
          </h1>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 lg:mx-0 sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl md:text-xl sm:text-lg dark:text-gray-300'
          >
            Astro Blog is a starter template written in Typescript, UnoCSS (using TailwindCSS
            directives), AlpineJS and Astro. It supports Markdown blog posts (including photo
            galleries), plus full text search.
          </p>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 lg:mx-0 sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl md:text-xl sm:text-lg dark:text-gray-300'
          >
            It has full SEO support for Facebook (Open Graph) tags, Twitter Cards and Schema/JSON-LD
            metadata. It also features fully auto generated RSS feed and sitemap for search engine
            indexing.
          </p>
          <div class='mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex lg:justify-start sm:justify-center'>
            <div class='rounded-md shadow'>
              <a
                href='/about'
                class='w-full flex items-center justify-center border border-transparent rounded-md bg-purple-600 px-8 py-3 text-base text-white font-medium dark:bg-purple-300 hover:bg-pink-600 md:px-10 md:py-4 md:text-lg dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-pink-300'
              >
                About
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class='mt-3 sm:ml-3 sm:mt-0'>
              <a
                href='https://github.com/sponsors/hellotham'
                class='w-full flex items-center justify-center border border-transparent rounded-md bg-purple-100 px-8 py-3 text-base text-purple-800 font-medium dark:bg-purple-900 hover:bg-pink-200 md:px-10 md:py-4 md:text-lg dark:text-purple-100 dark:hover:bg-pink-900'
                rel='noopener noreferrer'
                target='_blank'
              >
                Sponsor Us
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='bg-purple-100 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2 dark:bg-purple-500'>
    <Image
      class='h-56 w-full object-cover lg:h-full lg:w-full md:h-96 sm:h-72'
      src={DefaultImage}
      alt='a beautiful field of flowers next to a lake surrounded by mountains and trees at sunset'
    />
  </div>
</div>
